<view class="page-shell page-shell-tabbed">
  <view
    class="custom-nav-shell"
    style="padding-top: {{statusBarHeight}}px;"
  >
    <view class="custom-nav-panel" style="min-height: {{navPanelHeight}}px;">
      <view class="custom-nav-inner" style="height: {{navContentHeight}}px;">
        <view class="custom-nav-side" style="width: {{capsuleReserve}}px;"></view>
        <view class="custom-nav-title">LYC 首页</view>
        <view class="custom-nav-side" style="width: {{capsuleReserve}}px;"></view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
  <view class="custom-nav-spacer" style="height: {{navSpacerHeight}}px;"></view>

  <view class="hero-card hero-home fade-up">
    <view class="hero-glow hero-glow-left float-slow"></view>
    <view class="hero-glow hero-glow-right"></view>
    <text class="tag">小宇宙学堂</text>
    <view class="hero-title">今天想去哪里冒险？</view>
    <view class="hero-subtitle">
      从英语跟读到唐诗故事，把今天的 10 分钟变成有声音、有画面的学习旅程。
    </view>
    <view class="metric-row">
      <view class="metric-box">
        <text class="metric-value">{{totalStars}}</text>
        <text class="metric-label">成长星星</text>
      </view>
      <view class="metric-box">
        <text class="metric-value">{{streakDays}}</text>
        <text class="metric-label">连续学习</text>
      </view>
      <view class="metric-box">
        <text class="metric-value">4</text>
        <text class="metric-label">今日入口</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-head">
    <view>
      <view class="section-title">继续上次学习</view>
      <view class="section-caption">先接着上一次的节奏，孩子会更容易进入状态。</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="surface-card continue-card fade-up" bindtap="openContinue">
    <view class="continue-top">
      <view>
        <view class="continue-label">上次听到这里</view>
        <view class="continue-title">{{continueLesson.title}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="soft-chip">{{continueLesson.duration}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="continue-summary">{{continueLesson.summary}}</view>
    <view class="continue-bottom">
      <view class="continue-meta">
        <text class="soft-chip">{{continueLesson.ageRange}}</text>
        <text class="soft-chip">{{continueLesson.difficulty}}</text>
      </view>
      <view class="action-primary">继续学习</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-head">
    <view>
      <view class="section-title">四个冒险入口</view>
      <view class="section-caption">孩子先从喜欢的内容开始，学习体验会更轻松。</view>
    </view>
    <view class="section-link" bindtap="goDiscover">查看全部</view>
  </view>

  <view class="portal-grid">
    <portal-card
      wx:for="{{categories}}"
      wx:key="id"
      item="{{item}}"
      style="width: 48%; margin-bottom: 20rpx;"
      bind:select="openCategory"
    />
  </view>

  <view class="section-head">
    <view>
      <view class="section-title">今日推荐</view>
      <view class="section-caption">首版先给孩子安排一条节奏舒服的学习路线。</view>
    </view>
    <view class="section-link" bindtap="goGrowth">看成长</view>
  </view>

  <view class="list-block">
    <lesson-card
      wx:for="{{todayLessons}}"
      wx:key="id"
      item="{{item}}"
      bind:select="openLesson"
    />
  </view>

  <view class="section-head">
    <view>
      <view class="section-title">睡前轻听</view>
      <view class="section-caption">适合晚上放慢节奏，选一首诗或一个故事陪伴入睡前时光。</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="hero-card bedtime-card fade-up">
    <view class="bedtime-copy">
      <view class="bedtime-title">月光、小故事和轻轻的朗读</view>
      <view class="bedtime-text">
        睡前内容更适合“先听后说”，让孩子在放松状态下接受语言和知识。
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="list-block bedtime-list">
      <lesson-card
        wx:for="{{bedtimeLessons}}"
        wx:key="id"
        item="{{item}}"
        mode="compact"
        bind:select="openLesson"
      />
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
